<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #8b0000;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #8b0000;
      color: white !important;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #8b0000;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    .account-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .next-steps {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .next-steps li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to RedFlag!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container">
    <p>Hello <%= @lead_full_name %>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for creating your RedFlag account. We're excited to help you identify potential fraud, waste, and abuse in your financial data.</p>
    
    <div class="account-details">
      <h2>Your Account Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @lead_full_name %></p>
      <p><strong>Company:</strong> <%= @lead.company %></p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @lead.email %></p>
      <p><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= @lead.plan.humanize %></p>
      <% if @lead.newsletter? %>
        <p><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Subscribed</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    
    <div class="next-steps">
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Connect Your Data:</strong> Import your financial data through QuickBooks or CSV upload.</li>
        <li><strong>Run Analysis:</strong> Our AI algorithms will scan your data for suspicious patterns.</li>
        <li><strong>Review Results:</strong> Get a detailed report highlighting potential issues.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    
    <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="button">Get Started Now</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at support@redflagapp.com.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The RedFlag Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© 2025 RedFlag. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      This email was sent to <%= @lead.email %>. 
      If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can 
      <a href="#">unsubscribe</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>